        <item>
            <title>ASML 推出次世代曝光机　每部售价 3.8 亿美元比上代贵一倍</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/asml-shows-off-next-generation-380-million-high-na-euv-lithography-machines/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=asml-shows-off-next-generation-380-million-high-na-euv-lithography-machines</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/asml-shows-off-next-generation-380-million-high-na-euv-lithography-machines/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 10:00:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ASML]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[intel]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[半导体]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220541</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在晶片制造过程之中，曝光机是相当重要的存在，荷兰 ASML 就是这方面的龙头企业，最近正式公开 High-NA EUV 微影曝光设备，进一步提升晶片生产技术。<br /><span id="more-1220541"></span></p><p>ASML 早前终于向外界公开其次世代 TWINSCAN EXE:5000 曝光机（光刻机），采用新一代的 High-NA EUV 微影曝光技术，重量达到 165 公吨，造价 3.8 亿美元，是上代 Low-NA EUV 曝光机差不多 2 倍价钱。ASML 表示，新一代曝光机可以打印 8 纳米的图案，比上代密度提升 1.7 倍，每小时可生产 185 个晶圆。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0f8cd9c6d437fe5-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220542" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0f8cd9c6d437fe5-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/0f8cd9c6d437fe5.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这样庞大的机器需要由 250 名工程师在实地组装，而且需要 6 个月。去年 Intel 已经购入一部 TWINSCAN EXE:5000，不过在 2025 年之前都不会用于生产。而台积电方面仍然未有计划升级曝光机，可能正在等待更先进的产品推出才一次过投资，也就是 Hyper NA 技术，预计在 2030 年左右推出。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.extremetech.com/computing/asmls-shows-off-next-generation-380-million-high-na-euv-lithography-machines">Extreme Tech</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/05/win-10-too-old-hardware-cant-use-calculator/software/win10/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">旧电脑 Win 10 小算盘、相片无法启动，外媒：或因硬件太旧</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/tsmc-kaohsiung/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">台积电计划于高雄增设 2 纳米厂房　应付人工智能热潮下强劲需求</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/intel-ceo-gelsinger-says-china-is-ten-years-behind-in-chipmaking-capabilities/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Intel 总裁：中国晶片技术落后 10 年　可见将来不会改变</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/asml-shows-off-next-generation-380-million-high-na-euv-lithography-machines/fun-tech/">ASML 推出次世代曝光机　每部售价 3.8 亿美元比上代贵一倍</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
